<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF996A26FCFB93CF1D4FBD1F" blockId="98.[774,1369,1276,1700]" pageId="98" pageNumber="856">
Originally described in monotypic subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF996A26FCB693E41DB4BEEC" authorityName="Van Gelder" authorityYear="1959" box="[842,948,1469,1502]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Bauerus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="98" pageNumber="856" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Bauerus</taxonomicName>
