No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF996A26FF5E9ADE1D8EB62C" pageId="98" pageNumber="856" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF996A26FF5E9ADE1D8EB62C" blockId="98.[160,1369,1710,3478]" pageId="98" pageNumber="856">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF996A26FF5E9ADE1C09B79A" bold="true" box="[162,521,3207,3240]" pageId="98" pageNumber="856">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Near Threatened on The IUCN Red List. Although still widely distributed,it is locally uncommon, dependent upon highly fragile habitats, and is in significant decline (but at a rate of less than 30% over 15 years) due to human population density and habitat conversion.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
